description: Jalapeño Truck is Jacksonville's newest food truck bringing  Mexican street flavor at it's best. Fully loaded with the best mouth-watering food that will make you feel like you are having a authentic home made cooked meal in Mexico. The best from breakfast favorites like Chilaquiles, Huevos Rancheros to Enchiladas, Tortas, don't forget to enjoy your meal with a refreshing agua frescas. This Mexican food doesn't get more authentic than this!
name: Jalapeño Truck
